 expire and are", "bbox": [162.5, 969.5, 1106.8, 990.4]}, {"text": "expected to be fully refunded to us between 2020 and 2022 as a result of changes introduced by the TCJA. These", "bbox": [162.5, 994.5, 1106.1, 1015.4]}, {"text": "credit carryforwards are now reflected as taxes receivable within the deferred charges and other assets line item", "bbox": [162.5, 1019.5, 1093.5, 1040.4]}, {"text": "on our consolidated balance sheet. In addition, the Company has $5.5 million in remeasured charitable con-", "bbox": [162.5, 1044.5, 1060.9, 1065.4]}, {"text": "tribution carryforwards to offset future taxable income. The Company’s charitable contribution carryforwards", "bbox": [162.5, 1069.5, 1079.4, 1090.4]}, {"text": "expiration period begins in 2020.", "bbox": [162.5, 1094.5, 439.0, 1115.4]}, {"text": "The Company also has $33.3 million of state net operating loss carryforwards (net of $8.8 million of federal", "bbox": [204.2, 1132.0, 1106.6, 1152.9]}, {"text": "effects) and $1.8 million of state tax credits carryforwards (net of $0.5 million of federal effects). Depending on", "bbox": [162.5, 1157.0, 1097.2, 1177.9]}, {"text": "the jurisdiction in which the state net operating loss was generated, the carryforwards expiration period begins in", "bbox": [162.5, 1182.0, 1104.6, 1202.9]}, {"text": "2020.", "bbox": [162.5, 1207.0, 209.4, 1227.9]}, {"text": "We believe it is more likely than not that the benefit from certain state net operating loss carryforwards and", "bbox": [204.2, 1244.5, 1100.7, 1265.4]}, {"text": "state credit carryforwards will not be realized. Due to the uncertainty of realizing a benefit from the deferred tax", "bbox": [162.5, 1269.5, 1098.9, 1290.4]}, {"text": "asset recorded for the carryforwards, a valuation allowance of $1.8 million was established for the year ended", "bbox": [162.5, 1294.5, 1078.3, 1315.4]}, {"text": "September 30, 2019.", "bbox": [162.5, 1319.5, 335.1, 1340.4]}, {"text": "87", "bbox": [627.1, 1509.1, 647.9, 1529.9]}]}